                <p class="text-justify">Bangkok Airways is one of the regional airlines based in Bangkok, Thailand. The airline offers services to destinations like Thailand, Cambodia, China, Hong Kong, India, Laos, Malaysia, Maldives, Myanmar, Singapore, and Vietnam. Currently, the airline has a fleet of 35 aircraft and is known for its frequent flyer program called flyer bonus. </p>
